trans-unit.source: Provides data for the **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** event.
trans-unit.target: Gir dataene for den **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs class is used to supply event values to the **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** event and to enable you to specify a custom Windows identity for the current request.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs brukes til å oppgi hendelsen verdier for den **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** hendelsen, og slik at du kan angi en egendefinert Windows-ID for gjeldende forespørsel.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule> constructs a WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs object using the Windows identity supplied by IIS and the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> and passes it to the **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** event.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule>bygger en WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs-objekt som bruker Windows-identiteten som ble levert av IIS, og gjeldende <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>, og sender den til den **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** hendelsen.</xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule>

trans-unit.source: You can use the <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs.User%2A> property of the WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs object supplied to the **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** event to set the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> property of the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> to a custom <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> object.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke den <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs.User%2A>for WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs-objektet som er angitt for den **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** -hendelsen for å angi den <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>for gjeldende <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>til en egendefinert <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal>objektet.</xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> </xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs.User%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you do not specify a value for the <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs.User%2A> property during the **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** event, the Windows identity supplied by IIS is used as the identity for the current request.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du ikke angir en verdi for den <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs.User%2A>egenskapen under den **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** hendelsen Windows identiteten som ble levert av IIS brukes som identitet for gjeldende forespørsel.</xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs.User%2A>

trans-unit.source: If IIS uses anonymous authentication, then the <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs.Identity%2A> property is set to the identity returned by the <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity.GetAnonymous%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Hvis IIS bruker for anonym godkjenning, og deretter den <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs.Identity%2A>er satt til identiteten som ble returnert av den <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity.GetAnonymous%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity.GetAnonymous%2A> </xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs.Identity%2A>

trans-unit.source: The **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** event is raised only when the authentication <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthenticationSection.Mode%2A> is set to <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthenticationMode> and the <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule> is an active HTTP module for the application.
trans-unit.target: Den **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** hendelsen skjer bare når godkjenningen <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthenticationSection.Mode%2A>er satt til <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthenticationMode>og <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule>er en aktive HTTP-modul for applikasjonen.</xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthenticationMode> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthenticationSection.Mode%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a newly created instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer nyopprettede forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule> constructs a <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs> object using the Windows identity supplied by IIS and the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> and passes it to the **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** event.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule>bygger en <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs>objekt med Windows-identiteten som ble levert av IIS, og gjeldende <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>, og sender den til den **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** hendelsen.</xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs> </xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule>

trans-unit.source: The Windows identity object.
trans-unit.target: Windows identity-objekt.

trans-unit.source: The context for the event.
trans-unit.target: Konteksten for hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Web.HttpContext"></xref> object for the current HTTP request.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.Web.HttpContext"> </xref> objekt for den gjeldende HTTP-forespørsler.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> provides access to <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Request%2A>, <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Response%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> objects for the current request.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>gir tilgang til <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Request%2A>, <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Response%2A>, og <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>objekter for gjeldende forespørsel.</xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Response%2A> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Request%2A> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.HttpContext"></xref> object for the current HTTP request.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.HttpContext"> </xref> objekt for den gjeldende HTTP-forespørsler.

trans-unit.source: Gets the Windows identity passed to the <xref href="System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs"></xref> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Henter Windows-ID som er sendt til den <xref href="System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs"> </xref> konstruktør.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule> constructs a <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs> object using the Windows identity supplied by IIS and the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> and passes it to the **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** event.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule>bygger en <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs>objekt med Windows-identiteten som ble levert av IIS, og gjeldende <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>, og sender den til den **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** hendelsen.</xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs> </xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule>

trans-unit.source: If IIS uses anonymous authentication, the Identity property is set to the identity returned by the <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity.GetAnonymous%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Hvis IIS bruker for anonym godkjenning, Identitetsegenskapen er satt til identiteten som ble returnert av den <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity.GetAnonymous%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity.GetAnonymous%2A>

trans-unit.source: The Windows identity passed to the <xref href="System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs"></xref> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Windows-IDen som er sendt til den <xref href="System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs"> </xref> konstruktør.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> object to be associated with the current request.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal>objektet som skal knyttes til gjeldende forespørsel.</xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal>

trans-unit.source: You can use the User property to set the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> property of the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> to a custom <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> object.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke egenskapen for bruker til å angi den <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>for gjeldende <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>til en egendefinert <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal>objektet.</xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you do not specify a value for the User property during the **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** event, the Windows identity supplied by IIS is used as the identity for the current request.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du ikke angir en verdi for egenskapen for bruker i løpet av **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** hendelsen Windows identiteten som ble levert av IIS brukes som identitet for gjeldende forespørsel.

trans-unit.source: If IIS uses anonymous authentication, then the <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs.Identity%2A> property is set to the identity returned by the <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity.GetAnonymous%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Hvis IIS bruker for anonym godkjenning, og deretter den <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs.Identity%2A>er satt til identiteten som ble returnert av den <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity.GetAnonymous%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity.GetAnonymous%2A> </xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs.Identity%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> object to be associated with the current request.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal>objektet som skal knyttes til gjeldende forespørsel.</xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal>
